  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play the Right Card According to the Story's Progression</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a narrative-driven game that incorporates card-based gameplay. Featuring around 200 cards, the game follows a linear storyline where you must carefully read the plot description of each round, search for clues, and play the correct card to advance the story. Each round allows you to adjust part of your hand, and new plot developments will introduce new cards to help you deal with upcoming events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game features:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Logic and Judgment – Choose cards that fit the situation based on narrative hints</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3523990/extras/bb87c775a291f676dec8df298dd194de.avif?t=1751453036\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3523990/extras_big/bb87c775a291f676dec8df298dd194de.avif?t=1751453036 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic Deck Adjustment – You can replace some cards each turn and receive new story cards</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3523990/extras/548c07a0805ac4d50a753c0a827bd7ab.avif?t=1751453036\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3523990/extras_big/548c07a0805ac4d50a753c0a827bd7ab.avif?t=1751453036 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story Review – Revisit past plot points to trace clues and support your decisions</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3523990/extras/993631f3abfe6aa5f4ef84a9df9a65ff.avif?t=1751453036\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3523990/extras_big/993631f3abfe6aa5f4ef84a9df9a65ff.avif?t=1751453036 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Card Collection – Unlock and collect all cards featured in the story, and view detailed information about unlocked cards</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3523990/extras/875fbb3c2c235b9504817af352881b4e.avif?t=1751453036\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3523990/extras_big/875fbb3c2c235b9504817af352881b4e.avif?t=1751453036 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
